 former US President Bill Clinton says he should take a more backstage role should his wife , Hillary , decide to run for President .
In an interview with Town & Country Magazine , the 68-year-old revealed that he has lost his natural flair for political campaigning , adding that becoming a grandparent to his daughter Chelsea 's six-month-old daughter Charlotte has tamed the angry side of his personality .
Mrs Clinton is to launch her bid within the next two weeks .